<P><H1 align=center>WELCOME MENU – MN010</H1>
<P></P>
<P>This is the screen that appears when first logging on to Omiga. It comprises 
five areas: </P>
<P><H3>- Mortgage Calculator </H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P>OMIGA 4 includes a function for the calculation of mortgage repayment costs 
  </P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><H3>- Customer Registration </H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P>Customer Registration is the process of identifying or creating existing or 
  new Applicants and Applications. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><H3>- Application Enquiry </H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P>This allows the Users to locate their Mortgage Applications and enter the 
  OMIGA 4 system. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><H3>- Task Management </H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P>Also known as Mortgage Application Processing, covers the managed 
  progression of business activities that occur from Agreement In Principle data 
  capture to the Completion Stage. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><H3>- Payment Sanction </H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P>This area supports full payment creation, sanction, cancellation and return 
  of funds - Click on the relevant button to get the required area of the 
  system. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>
